Definition: marked by lack of attention or consideration or forethought or thoroughness
Example: not careful; careless about her clothes; forgotten by some careless person; a careless housekeeper; careless proofreading; it was a careless mistake; hurt by a careless remark
Synonyms: noun, attribute, carelessness, act, CAREFUL, IMPRUDENT, INATTENTIVE, INCAUTIOUS, NEGLIGENT, SUPERFICIAL, UNCONCERNED, carefulness, marked, by, lack, of, attention, or, consideration, forethought, thoroughness, not, careful, careless, about, her, clothes, forgotten, some, person, a, housekeeper, proofreading, it, was, mistake, hurt, remark
Category: adj.all
